{"tid":1581438,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［真攬炒？］台山核電廠外電網前日故障 反應堆曾停運 廠方：對公眾無影響","createTime":"2019-09-19T14:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T15:02:31.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ef4cea135c2434e4a05e52262d5cbf92c7c43b","tid":1581438,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"保安局引述台山核電合營有限公司通報，台山核電廠一號機組本周二（17號）晚上8時8分發生「0級事件」，外電網輸電線路出現短暫故障，反應堆自動安全停運。運行人員立即按程序穩定機組狀態。<br />\n<br />\n該公司指，根據國際原子能機構的國際核和放射事件分級表，有關事件被評定為「非等級核電站運行事件」（即「0級」事件），對電站的安全運作、員工健康及附近地區的公眾和環境並無任何影響。台山核電站所有機組現保持安全穩定運行。公眾可於網站（<a href=\"http://www.tnpjvc.com.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tnpjvc.com.cn&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP0ad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=d445c21d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.tnpjvc.com.cn</a>）的「企業與社會」內的「安全信息」內的「運行事件」分頁上查閱事件。不過該網英文版本並無相關紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n台山核電廠上月20日也曾發生0級事件，當日下午4時50分安全廠房兩個送風風門不能遠端控制，不符技術要求，系統功能最終於下午5時46分恢復正常。國際核和放射事件分級表將核電問題分為1至7級，1至3級為事件，4至7級為事故，0級屬異常需糾正偏差。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190919/60062828?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60062828%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP0ad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=93518c7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60062828%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=98da8a7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190919/60062828?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"84dc6e51aeaea51145bf47227384bdf3ffa07ef7","tid":1581438,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c814bb0ad20763450dbf71043e63cd2e3a4633b","tid":1581438,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"e00e4c4417313410e1536dd85f55136177edfb93","tid":1581438,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}